
Required Libraries

** Available as Debian packages ** 
SDL
SDL_net
SDL_ttf
SDL_image
GL
GLU
ossp-uuid++ (NOTE: when installing from ossp uuid++ form source, be sure to configure with ./configure --with-cxx, so that c++ bindings are included


** Required Downloads ** 

Makepp
http://makepp.sourceforge.net/

** Included but not built libraries **
Jsoncpp
homepage: http://jsoncpp.sourceforge.net/
svn: svn co https://jsoncpp.svn.sourceforge.net/svnroot/jsoncpp jsoncpp


** OS X ** 
All libraries listed above must be built from source.